Package courses

Class Course

java.lang.Object
courses.Course
public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a course. It contains a course id, description, several sessions inside the course, the students in the course, the faculties teaching the course and the minimum and maximum number of students allowed to join the course.
Since:
: 12/01/2020

      public Course​(java.lang.String courseId, java.lang.String courseCode, java.lang.String description, int numOfSessions, int max, int min)
      Constructor for the course object. It will initialize basic information about the course like, name, id, min and max students allowed. It will also initialze the list of students, sessions, and faculty
      Parameters:
      courseId - : the id of the course
      courseCode - : course code
      description - : description of the course
      numOfSessions - : number of sessions initially scheduled in course
      max - : max number of students in course
      min - : minimum number of students
